  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is intended for absolute hemolysis level prediction supporting a Class III VAD submission at Model Risk Level 5. Thirteen credibility factors are evaluated; seven are assessed and six are flagged as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was performed. All assessed factors achieved required levels under the Minimal profile review scope. Decision: Accepted under Minimal profile with acknowledged factor gaps documented in the decision record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-hemolysis-cfd-claim-001",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/fda-centrifugal-pump-cfd-v2",
